OL,3,C'Hero' rescues disabled man from
OL,4,C'fireball' car
OL,6,FJulie Griffiths and Garry Smith were
OL,7,Freunited with Michael Gardiner days
OL,8,Fafter his heroic intervention. Helen
OL,9,FSteel went to meet them
OL,11,FThe sister of a severely disabled man
OL,12,Fhas described a passerby who rescued
OL,13,Fher brother moments before their car
OL,14,Fburst into flames as a "hero".
OL,16,FJulie Griffiths was taking her
OL,17,Fbrother, Garry Smith, back to his care
OL,18,Fhome in Calverley, near Leeds, when
OL,19,Fher car's engine overheated.
