OL,3,C'Hero' rescues disabled man from
OL,4,C'fireball' car
OL,6,FJulie and Garry, who has cerebral
OL,7,Fpalsy and is deaf and partially
OL,8,Fsighted, had been on a day trip when
OL,9,Fsmoke started coming from the car's
OL,10,Fengine as the drove along the Leeds
OL,11,Fring road.
OL,13,FJulie said: "Within 30 seconds it got
OL,14,Freally bad. Somebody shouted 'move'. I
OL,15,Fcan't remember a lot after that.
