OL,3,C'Hero' rescues disabled man from
OL,4,C'fireball' car
OL,6,F"I don't like to be called a hero. I
OL,7,Fjust did what I hope anyone would do
OL,8,Fif I was in that situation. I just
OL,9,Fhappened to be there at the right
OL,10,Ftime."
OL,12,FIn a Facebook post, New Farnley
OL,13,FCricket Club praised Mr Gardiner's
OL,14,Factions.
