OL,3,C'Hero' rescues disabled man from
OL,4,C'fireball' car
OL,6,FThe post said: "Whilst everyone else
OL,7,Fdrove past, he noticed that the
OL,8,Fpassenger was a disabled man. He duly
OL,9,Fpulled up his car and with the help of
OL,10,Fanother heroic man dragged the man
OL,11,Ffrom the car into safety of the
OL,12,Fadjacent bus layby.
OL,14,F"Seconds later the car exploded. The
OL,15,Fbravery saved the man's life."
